Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏意正濃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高一的夏天一天天過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也意味著 挑戰富士山的日子越來越近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 再拖拖拉拉就丟下你不管囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.11,0:01:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.46,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向河出發？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一整天在游泳池泡著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體育課就夠了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小葵 放學之後跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好·地·方！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的好地方就是飯能河原？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是經常來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:25.30,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯能河原，位於飯能站步行約15分鐘的入間川河畔。\N春夏可進行燒烤、露營、郊遊散步，冬天紅葉風景秀美。\N 距東京市中心只有1小時車程，是東京、琦玉的戶外休閒熱門地點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 在橋對面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋對面？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 還沒到？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上 馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去入間川上游的吾妻峽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾妻峽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都走半個小時了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 是個好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.95,0:03:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空氣好清新啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼好的地方 竟然走路就能到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上一定還有更多這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在游泳肯定不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哆來咪發唆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你倒是等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 下次找來可可娜醬和小楓學姐一起來游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爬富士山 沒有體力怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當鍛鍊身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴上這麼說 其實只是你想游泳而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這樣好了 大家穿上性感的泳衣集合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼樣的泳衣才算是性感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家可是只有學校的泳衣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感 性感…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不想了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要零食？ 冰箱裡有布丁喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,xi…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,xi？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感的泳衣是什麼樣的 這種問題怎麼問得出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,xi… 西武有沒有領先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.08,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西武獅隊 琦玉縣的職業棒球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵你什麼時候對棒球感興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感的泳衣 性感的泳衣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒概念
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵都高中生了 連件性感的泳衣都穿不上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說你 長不大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.48,0:06:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個臭日向 區區性感泳衣 誰不能穿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感 性感…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這哪都遮不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這繩子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝的泳衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這衣架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣式也太多了 怎麼選啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人 您買泳衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 想買件有點…性感…的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.48,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小葵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要去吾妻峽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐和可可娜醬也都答應了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了穿性感泳衣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待啊 那明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個臭日向！給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15號颱風正在接近 速度逐漸變快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計將於後半夜在關東地區登陸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這泳算是游不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天晴了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颱風過境
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但河水卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是游不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天還是撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說笨蛋不感冒 原來這是迷信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些波折 但幾天之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些陰天 但氣溫也很高 適合玩水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性感泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然穿在裡面了 但果然好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來游吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你們不脫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐 不脫衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您先脫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位肯定是不好意思穿性感泳衣見人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然確實是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我不會游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為小楓學姐什麼運動都會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高估我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那曬個日光浴也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就日光浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超涼的 這水溫游不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是流水 所以河水跟泳池不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算氣溫高 水溫也會很低
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天陰天 太陽公公也沒出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有地下水匯流進去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定水溫很低呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天氣在河裡游泳肯定又要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於晴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別盯著看啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會很怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 小葵這也不算性感嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.52,0:10:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就為這個害羞了半天？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家沒穿過露臍裝的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可娜醬比我開放啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員推薦這件 就買了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓學姐的泳衣也很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.83,0:11:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不是我想買的 但朋友非要我買這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向你怎麼還穿著外衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看我的性感泳衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校泳衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算哪門子性感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿上就夠性感啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ฅ•ω•ฅ)♡喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵你個頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 雖然沒在吾妻峽玩到水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又多了一次夏天愉快的回憶！
